rows.label: qst101201_msg0002
rows.name:
Grannypon leave veg-veg
seeds to Umama, so Umama
want to grow new veg-veg.

rows.label: qst101201_msg0003
rows.name:
But noooo! Veg-veg soooo delicate!
Not want to grow for Umama!

rows.label: qst101201_msg0004
rows.name:
Well... In perfect world,
Umama give veg-veg lots and
lots of fertilizer...

rows.label: qst101201_msg0005
rows.name:
But Umama just getting started,
have no veg-veg to sell, cannot
afford expensive poo-poo.

rows.label: qst101201_msg0006
rows.name:
Maybe it best if Umama give up.
With apologies to Grannypon...

rows.label: qst101201_msg0007
rows.name:
Mo? Friends help Umama?
Yippee! Umama super happy!

rows.label: qst101201_msg0008
rows.name:
When veg-veg grow, friends
first in line to taste!

rows.label: qst101201_msg0009
rows.name:
If friends find thing that work
as fertilizer, give Umama shout!

rows.label: qst101201_msg0010
rows.name:
And if thing nutritious, well,
then we not need so many!

rows.label: qst101201_msg0101
rows.name:
Friends bring fertilizer?
Value of nutrition differ
from thing to thing.

rows.label: qst101201_msg0110
rows.name:
Still need more nutrition!
Bring more fertilizer!

rows.label: qst101201_msg0120
rows.name:
Nutrition level now perfect!
Umama thank friends!

rows.label: qst101201_msg0121
rows.name:
Now we leave veg-veg to
grow big. Friends have
napperoo, then come see!

rows.label: qst101201_msg0201
rows.name:
Thank friends for help! Plenty
fertilizer, plenty nutrition!

rows.label: qst101201_msg0202
rows.name:
Now we leave veg-veg to
grow big. Friends have
napperoo, then come see!
